{"tid":333610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【迷魂黨出沒？】中國女中環行過撞一撞 港男一索濃烈異味即頭暈","createTime":"2017-07-24T03:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T03:47:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"813712885cd4c67a3c6006fcda214778d219540b","tid":333610,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"晚上6時許，一名35歲姓顏男子報稱在中環環球大廈附近與一內地女子發生碰撞，其間他嗅到一陣濃烈的氣味後感到頭暈，於是向附近的食環署職員求助報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報趕到，但發現事主所指的女子已離去，經調查後相信共有兩女一男操普通話的疑人涉案，案發時他們曾向男事主揮動一紙巾，事主吸入氣味後感不適。男事主並無損失，惟需送院治理。案件暫列危害生命或使人身體受嚴重傷害而使用毒藥，交由中區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56993851&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56993851%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170723&d=TzwoJHWTriFuWeEjUIPEWRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0447e0d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56993851%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170723&h=1a59a7e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56993851&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170723</a>"},{"pid":"b6a542075aa54ea9c65a763b71f5a153593c29ea","tid":333610,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850b553f5a521eaf6427da0145cc3a72cd991f9d","tid":333610,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1da6a4c4957b48534d7a10f6de4c83efe81adbaa","tid":333610,"uid":96871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:36:17.000Z","m